<article id="intro" class="grid_12-12">
	<h1>What it is</h1>
	<p>The Scalable Grid System or <a href="http://scalable.gs" title="Scalable Grid System">scalable.gs</a> for short, is a device independent and cross screen size web development framework.</p>
	<p>It follows up on the main ideas from the <a href="http://960.gs" title="The 960 grid system">960.gs</a>, but makes it fluid like <a href="http://cssgrid.net/" title="CSS Grid">cssgrid.net</a>. It is topped off with some of the thoughts behind <a href="http://jquerymobile.com/" title="jQuery Mobile">jQuery Mobile</a> in addition to some custom mobile UX design.</p>
</article>

